      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BANK KEEPING (4) turned in a strong performance after stalking the pace to win by 1.75 lengths at this track over 320m (18.37) in a Grade 5. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Well placed and will be tough to beat. SECRET BULLET (2) has a terrific record this track and trip with two wins and one placing from three starts. In the money last time at this track (18.73) in a Grade 5, finishing a 5 length third. Among the main chances. RAMSET READY (1) settled down midfield and held her position to the line when finishing 4th (18.73) at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can measure up this time.",
